{"tid":1217453,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想再食煙了。","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:29:14.000Z","uid":207380,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4348054ed84cd253c8cc0e151baee23a240805","tid":1217453,"uid":207380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"致各位想戒煙的你：<br />\n小弟不才，前天吃了4、5支煙已經想死。<br />\n回到家，夢見周公，介紹環保戒煙方法予我。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">在此分享予大家參考</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望幫到大家戒煙，唔得求下你地唔屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑鳩我好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當我白癡仔啦。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為我都未試過</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\">做個環保人仕。</span>"},{"pid":"bd6431ab06d47180aa1f9ed698ce914ca469e922","tid":1217453,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:12:36.000Z","msg":"咩書黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bf23b91868558708ab4bdcb7e10186ba276c81","tid":1217453,"uid":240436,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bd6431ab06d47180aa1f9ed698ce914ca469e922","tid":1217453,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:12:36.000Z","msg":"咩書黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TM8U8sT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i